item.description:
Chinese New Year is next week, so let's celebrate by having a little (or a lot) of Chinese food.  The Great Buffet II really is a great buffet.  The sushi alone is worth the price of the buffet, on top of that they have a nice cold seafood bar, a salad bar, several rows of Chinese and American foods.  Occasionally they'll have specials on lobster and bottled beer.

Join us for some Chinese food and lets ring in the year of the Dragon.
